def: Disposed to fly away; flighty; unrestrained; light and free; --used of both persons and things. -- n.
An electric generator or dynamo for producing alternatingcurrents.
Full of, or prone to, revenge; vindictive; malicious;revenging; wreaking revenge.If thy revengeful heart can not forgive. Shak.May my hands . . . Never brandish more rebvengeful steel. Shak.
The state or quality of being legitimate; lawfulness;genuineness.
Having the form of a tear; tear-shaped.
